ce th=E8me <a href=3D"http://topolearnnips2007.insa-rouen.fr/">http://topol=
earnnips2007.insa-rouen.fr/</a>).</span></font></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'text-autospace:none'><font size=3D2 face=3D"C=
